  <brief_title>Placebo Effect in the Treatment of Atopic Dermatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Placebo Effect in Atopic Dermatitis - Increase the Pharmacological Effect of Itching Caused by Classical Conditioning and Expectancy Processes: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
