  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is initiated in the indication of atopic dermatitis to study the impact of placebo
      in the treatment of pruritus. Classical conditioning and anticipation maintain the effect of
      placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
